{"tid":555852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本研究：每月加班逾60小時 員工更感幸福更愛公司","createTime":"2018-02-10T02:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T12:28:56.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"91a6bce8876ff2596999efa5095dd843500a7e16","tid":555852,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T02:16:03.000Z","msg":"日本一項研究指出，每月加班超過60小時，幸福感會上升，對公司的好感也會增加！<br />\n<br />\n日本Persol綜合研究所與東京大學副教授中原俊于，去年10月就加班進行研究，發現隨著加班時間增加，快樂度會逐漸減少，員工健康風險也會增加。但進一步的調查卻發現，若每月加班60小時以上，員工的幸福感居然會上升，對公司的滿意度和工作動力也會增加。<br />\n<br />\n調查訪問了6000名僱員，結果顯示加班1至10小時，幸福指數最高，有18.58分，若加班45至60小時，幸福指數跌到最低，只有16.98分。但奇怪的是，當加班超過60小時，幸福指數又回升至17.54分。<br />\n<br />\n在日本，加班過勞致死的問題日益嚴峻。去年底，一名女職員連續兩個月加班110和120小時，最後在工作中猝死。員工每月若加班超過80小時，便超越所謂的「過勞死紅線」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180210/57815231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180210%2F57815231&d=9kWRrrbm%2Fk7%2Bxn%2BO0qEwoDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=2c08b565\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180210%2F57815231&h=57a651e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180210/57815231</a>"},{"pid":"109669d0fb84497d3f12c5c4076ecb77c9739536","tid":555852,"uid":39800,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"幾時日本研究取代左英國研究"},{"pid":"be81d9ec1a965f8038fed282ae327498a51f2985","tid":555852,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T02:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4093b3df496a8f1e87c9842ecd1e0f8a8c1f86