.000Z","msg":"因為唔使諗放工之後有咩做,<br />\n唔會覺得孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,<br />\n放假又有藉口好攰要休息留返係屋企，<br />\n又有藉口好攰唔做家務唔使湊仔推晒比老婆，<br />\n我舊老細就係人辦，<br />\n放工唔走睇淘寶睇甜網預岩時間返到屋企開飯時間<br />\n超幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46489008ad179ed0c74a43201bc531a20b9e9c8f","tid":555852,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"109669d0fb84497d3f12c5c4076ecb77c9739536","tid":555852,"uid":39800,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"幾時日本研究取代左英國研究"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fef52232a6a2e7920d4eb73a95d031fb4eb526","tid":555852,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"唔怪得冇人信專家權威同研究,全部都係資本家既打手黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3819f55a1023fd824a5d10159b0ba7fe28648123","tid":555852,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}